transcript: I'm homeless and desperately need shelter. I've been on the streets for 3 months.
I can't afford food for my kids. We're going hungry and I don't know what to do.
I lost my job last month and need help finding employment. I have construction experience.
I need medical care but have no insurance. My diabetes is getting worse.
I'm facing eviction and also lost my job. Need help with both housing and employment.
I need help with childcare so I can go to work. My kids are 3 and 5.
I'm a veteran and need help with PTSD treatment and finding work.
My car broke down and I can't get to work. Need help with transportation.
I'm escaping domestic violence and need a safe place to stay immediately.
I can't afford my medications and my health is declining. Need prescription assistance.
